import React from 'react'
import { Button } from '../Button/Button'
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'
import "./Navbar.css"
import Dropdown from '../Dropdown/Dropdown'

function Navbar() {

        <>
         <nav className='navbar'>
            <Link to='/' className='navbar-logo'>
                JKT
            </Link>   
         </nav>

}

export default Navbar
